Message.message: Sort the blocks so each row of the grid contains only the same type of block. (Or you can sort by column.)
Move the cursor with the arrow keys and press X to select a block. Swap that block with one next to it using the arrow keys or hit X to cancel.
Long blocks can only move horizontally, and tall blocks can only move vertically.
Press R to reset with a new puzzle.
